{"tid":2516988,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"居港外國人掀離港潮 半山區租金高位跌25%","createTime":"2021-05-05T04:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T05:42:08.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"49dd76f9165c6c797c80c5c9adf02b6f7263351c","tid":2516988,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T04:35:51.000Z","msg":"《彭博》報道，自反修例運動爆發後，掀起居港外籍人士的離港潮，加上人口下降、失業率高企等因素，使香港租屋需求下跌。中原地產數據顯示，今年首季本港私人住宅實用面積的平均租金，已回落至每平方呎33.6港元，為2016年底以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n雖然本港首季經濟按年升7.8%，但3月份失業率仍高達6.8%，不少失業人士退租與家人同住。租屋網站千居（Spacious）數據亦顯示，半山區、深水灣等外國人及內地富豪熱捧地區，高級住宅租金已較2019年中高位，下跌25%；備受外國學生、年輕白領鍾愛的上環蘇豪區，租金同期則跌20%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/IYXPDCY6JRBH5ENQN43NMNIXVU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FIYXPDCY6JRBH5ENQN43NMNIXVU%2F&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=8d844d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210505%2FIYXPDCY6JRBH5ENQN43NMNIXVU%2F&h=e1aa49aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210505/IYXPDCY6JRBH5ENQN43NMNIXVU/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2021-05-05/hong-kong-rents-drop-amid-foreign-exodus-video\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2F2021-05-05%2Fhong-kong-rents-drop-amid-foreign-exodus-video&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK1LdO2JNS7rEhaOnhOWKq7w%3D&h=04dede85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2021-05-05/hong-kong-rents-drop-amid-foreign-exodus-video</a>"},{"pid":"0874e948f49c020397a70165f43d269f3448817f","tid":2516988,"uid":152705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T04:37:54.000Z","msg":"全港玩埋21日隔離 , 點頂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class